{"tid":1451933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得要做定文宣   警告港人會有狗被政府暗殺嫁禍示威者","createTime":"2019-08-11T22:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T18:09:28.000Z","uid":189150,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3087a0b1c43575edac147bebb495f7b1cd1c1e68","tid":1451933,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:07:44.000Z","msg":"去到呢個地步  基本上都肯定有武警介入香港事務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到今晚有多名示威者重傷，盲眼<br />\n淺藍淺黃民意已經完全傾向示威者個面  （深藍絲個d不是民意，無需理會，香港比中國放核彈佢地都會覺得中國做得岩）<br />\n下一步要搶民意，無可否認既，就係要有狗嚴重受傷甚至死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後警嫂出黎喊到呼天搶地，再盛大浩園葬禮<br />\n<br />\n中共去到呢個地步，極高機會會搵一兩個警犬出黎搞到重傷，係極高機會！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要守住民意，我覺得做文宣既要先警告港人佢地會出呢個劇本<br />\n等到時台戲上時衝擊細d，比大家有個心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af5f44e45c569509b86bd3fd9fb16010b64c7e3","tid":1451933,"uid":274294,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:12:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n總之有狗死就係港共殺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcd2318fd6904ccff4886fdb9295c79b729a810","tid":1451933,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:15:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"618c908e7a250664a95718a0dfbbaffe90bfb07d","tid":1451933,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地就係你地嘅報應<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aab9bbada28c64cab52ef2823cfb5c7ea578ef5e","tid":1451933,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:18:53.000Z","msg":"啱 班狗真係咩都做得出"},{"pid":"9cd5c10408ab56f8f267e9aa3e4001f52c6897d9","tid":1451933,"uid":189150,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:35:04.000Z","msg":"比市民心理準備好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果俾佢地搶先，好容易完全轉風向<br />\n尤其tvb威力好大<br />\n大家諗下如果有狗死，tvb實收order日日播特輯<br />\n特別新聞播幾個鐘<br />\n每日朝早，午間，晚間都播片段，播下警嫂狗同胞點喊<br />\n東張西望日日報葬禮安排<br />\n六日整個專訪<br />\n日日直播政府出黎表示痛心<br />\n葬禮又直播<br />\n追悼會又直播<br />\n搵堆愛國人士示威喊親飽又直播<br />\n我肯定民意會轉<br />\n<br />\n如果大家可以做定民宣，真係會差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21aa0c5f322b1f299ef431477534515082b1c6","tid":1451933,"uid":189150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:49:46.000Z","msg":"再留意下央視新聞<br />\n尋晚已經報導左 警員比汽油彈燒傷 可能要截肢乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n剩係報狗受傷屈鳩示威者，當然係用黎帶輿論<br />\n但要留意既係平時邊有報得咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n合理懷疑呢單係用黎試水溫，鋪路之後有狗死<br />\n之後就會出黎話示威者武力一路升級，由咬斷手指，爆頭骨，到而家截肢，再控制唔到輿論既話，一定就係狗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8ae403e1cfe833e313ec70d86aae4fcbbd7e47","tid":1451933,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:02:26.000Z","msg":"分分鐘隔離post 啲巴打係中共做野之前已經殺左幾件"},{"pid":"8fd70b010b5297540406945d621a12c0a5da8afb","tid":1451933,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:03:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c864520c9fcf4dad2d0cbb29e7a222b8b629cb98","tid":1451933,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28a6ce81ff2f906336112ad1947294db989440d1","tid":1451933,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:21:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ab85d15565f569bb6e998993a0f5338475c36d6","tid":1451933,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8ae403e1cfe833e313ec70d86aae4fcbbd7e47","tid":1451933,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike"